Title: Back to Reality
Description:
We were able to increase Ambassador Chronormu's connection to our time. I am certain when we find her again, we will be able to finish the ritual.

For now, let us return to our present and a world with... significantly fewer murlocs.
ObjectivesText: Return to Nozdormu in the Present.
RewardText: Thank you for helping to uphold the timelines... odd as they may sometimes be.
